tell her not to do anything.

269
00:17:18,704 --> 00:17:23,041
Thanks for sticking up for me.
God, you are such a nice person.

270
00:17:24,376 --> 00:17:25,418
I try.

271
00:17:59,036 --> 00:18:00,745
Oh!

272
00:18:03,415 --> 00:18:08,503
