273
00:18:09,338 --> 00:18:11,130
Thank you!

274
00:18:13,383 --> 00:18:15,093
You're welcome.

275
00:18:27,773 --> 00:18:29,774
Wow! You look...

276
00:18:30,692 --> 00:18:32,944
